			"condition": "",
			"prompt": "<anim cat='emoji' filter='thanksgiving, !hot-frame' layers='!audio' nonBlocking='true'/>Thanksgiving dinner is one of the few times I do wish I could eat. It seems fun.",
			"media": "TTS",
